Individual




Michael B. Richings



Mr. Michael B. Richings is Independent Director at Guyana Goldfields, Inc. and Non-Executive Chairman at Vista Gold Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Guyana Goldfields, Inc.
Mr. Richings was previously employed as Independent Director by Midas Gold Corp., President by Lac Minerals Ltd., President & Chief Executive Officer by Atlas Corp., and President by Lac South America. He also served on the board at Allied Nevada Gold Corp., Zaruma Resources, Inc., and Triumph Gold Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from the Camborne School of Mines and a graduate degree from Queen's University.



